---
import StaticLayout from '@layouts/StaticLayout.astro';
---

<StaticLayout title="FAQ">
  <h1 slot="header" class="font-serif uppercase text-pink text-[10rem]">FAQ</h1>
  <section slot="main" class="md:pr-5 lg:pr-24">
    <ul class="space-y-10">
      <li class="space-y-1.5">
        <div class="flex text-pink uppercase text-xl tracking-[0.1rem]">
          <span class="leading-8">Q.&nbsp;</span>
          <h class="leading-8"2>Will there be options for guests with dietary restrictions or allergies?</h>
        </div>
        <div class="flex uppercase text-xl tracking-[0.1rem]">
          <span class="leading-8">A.&nbsp;</span>
          <p class="leading-8">Yes, we want to accommodate all our guests. Please let us know about any dietary restrictions or allergies when you RSVP, and our catering team will provide suitable meal options.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="space-y-1.5">
        <div class="flex text-pink uppercase text-xl tracking-[0.1rem]">
          <span class="leading-8">Q.&nbsp;</span>
          <h class="leading-8"2>Can I see the menu in advance?</h>
        </div>
        <div class="flex uppercase text-xl tracking-[0.1rem]">
          <span class="leading-8">A.&nbsp;</span>
          <p class="leading-8">Certainly! We'll be sharing the menu details on our wedding website or in the invitations so you can plan accordingly.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="space-y-1.5">
        <div class="flex text-pink uppercase text-xl tracking-[0.1rem]">
          <span class="leading-8">Q.&nbsp;</span>
          <h class="leading-8"2> Is there a vegetarian or vegan meal option available?</h>
        </div>
        <div class="flex uppercase text-xl tracking-[0.1rem]">
          <span class="leading-8">A.&nbsp;</span>
          <p class="leading-8">Absolutely, we will have delicious vegetarian and vegan meal choices to cater to our guests with dietary preferences.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="space-y-1.5">
        <div class="flex text-pink uppercase text-xl tracking-[0.1rem]">
          <span class="leading-8">Q.&nbsp;</span>
          <h class="leading-8"2>Can I request a specific dish or customize my meal?</h>
        </div>
        <div class="flex uppercase text-xl tracking-[0.1rem]">
          <span class="leading-8">A.&nbsp;</span>
          <p class="leading-8">While we can't accommodate individual dish requests, we'll provide a variety of meal options to suit different tastes.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="space-y-1.5">
        <div class="flex text-pink uppercase text-xl tracking-[0.1rem]">
          <span class="leading-8">Q.&nbsp;</span>
          <h class="leading-8"2>What is the timeline for dinner service?</h>
        </div>
        <div class="flex uppercase text-xl tracking-[0.1rem]">
          <span>A.&nbsp;</span>
          <p>Dinner service will begin at [insert time], and we'll ensure there's ample time for everyone to enjoy their meal and celebrate with us.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</StaticLayout>